    {
      "id": "1442131015081529435",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-11-23T12:33:47.494+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Looking at the rule:\n\n```\n  # Rule M3.2b: Space to wide Metal3 (length & width > 10um) is 0.3\u00b5m\n  logger.info('Executing rule M3.2b')\n  wide_m3 = metal3.not_interacting(metal3.edges.with_length(nil, 10.um))\n  m32b_l1 = metal3.separation(wide_m3, 0.3.um, euclidian)\n  m32b_l1.output('M3.2b', 'M3.2b : Space to wide Metal3 (length & width > 10um) : 0.3\u00b5m')\n  m32b_l1.forget\n  wide_m3.forget\n```",
      "author": {
        "id": "732347216412278825",
        "name": "urish",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "urish",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [
          {
            "id": "1423020172595298314",
            "name": "Mod",
            "color": null,
            "position": 1
          }
        ],
        "avatarUrl": "2025-11_media/2b6c3aac0ae09fc8a72a4b2e17d7f9c9-39032.png"
